CustomField.formula: IF(AND(VALUE(MID( FW_END_DATE__c , 5, 2)) >=1 , VALUE(MID( FW_END_DATE__c , 5, 2)) <=3),"Q1", IF(AND(VALUE(MID( FW_END_DATE__c , 5, 2)) >=4 , VALUE(MID( FW_END_DATE__c , 5, 2)) <=6),"Q2", IF( AND(VALUE(MID( FW_END_DATE__c , 5, 2)) >=7 , VALUE(MID( FW_END_DATE__c , 5, 2))<=9),"Q3","Q4"))) & Fiscal_Year__c
CustomField.label: Fiscal Quarter
